Following this, an investigating consciousness arises, a wholesome-resultant or unwholesome-resultant citta which investigates the object; then a determining consciousness, a functional citta which defines the object; and then comes a string of cittas called javana, which constitute either a wholesome or an unwholesome response to the object.
